text: AudioBook Generator 1. Introduction / Objective  AudioBook Generator is a web application that allows users to upload one or more text documents (PDF, DOCX, TXT) and automatically converts them into high-quality audiobooks. The application leverages Large Language Models (LLMs) to rewrite extracted text in an engaging, listener-friendly “audiobook style” before using open-source Text-to- Speech (TTS) technology to produce downloadable audio files. This project enhances accessibility, productivity, and the enjoyment of written content.
